HEADWORD: Burghbote
<hw>Burgh"bote`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Burgh</ets> + <ets>bote</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Old Law)</fld>
<def>A contribution toward the building or repairing of castles or walls
for the defense of a city or town.</def>⟦br⟧
